---
title: Italian Sausage and Pesto Flatbreads with Balsamic-Dressed Garden Salad
description: Italian sausage sautéed with onions is a perfect topper for pesto-coated flatbreads! Finish with a sprinkling of mozzarella and Parm before transferring it to the oven for some melting action. A refreshing salad drizzled with balsamic glaze rounds out this delicious dinner!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pains-plats-a-la-saucisse-italienne-et-au-pesto-22ef828a.jpg
